name: Dr. Evelyn Reed
subject: Physics
bio: PhD in Quantum Physics, Dr. Reed is passionate about making complex concepts accessible and inspiring the next generation of scientists.

name: Mr. Samuel Chen
subject: History
bio: A historian with a focus on world cultures, Mr. Chen brings history to life with engaging stories and interactive lessons.

name: Ms. Aisha Khan
subject: Mathematics
bio: Ms. Khan believes in building strong foundational skills and uses innovative methods to make math enjoyable and understandable for all students.

name: Mr. Benjamin Carter
subject: Literature
bio: An avid reader and writer, Mr. Carter fosters a love for literature by exploring classic and contemporary works with his students.

name: Ms. Isabella Rossi
subject: Art
bio: A professional artist, Ms. Rossi encourages creativity and self-expression through various mediums, from painting to digital art.

name: Mr. Omar Abdullah
subject: Computer Science
bio: With a background in software development, Mr. Abdullah equips students with cutting-edge coding skills and a deep understanding of technology.
